72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1439&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=70d7d0ed5acc9583acb94c195c8a685a 2000w"
                    />

            
    
